S5.title: 12 hour☘️ Study with me LIVE ☕ calm cozy ambience🩺POMODORO🔥Real-time study #Medgirl 2025-04-03 15:44
S5.description:
📩open me:

Hi!
Welcome to another Study with me
Thanks for joining
_________________________

I hope this study video helps you avoid using social media while you study. You will find a quiet and cosy study room ambience in this video when studying at your home. Hopefully, this would get you motivated more for studying. You might hear the rain, birds, typing sounds and the flipping of pages (and cars too, unfortunately) from time to time, and I hope that helps you know that I'm there studying with you!

🔥Key to success - """"BE CONSISTENT""""🔥

___________________________

What are you studying and where are you joining from? I also wonder what type of videos you like, study at the library or study at home? Your opinions are quite important to me; and, if you let me know what type of videos you like to watch, I would be happy. 
_____________________________

✧･ﾟ at the beginning of the study sessions, make sure to:
- turn off anything you're not going to be using to study
- have your materials ready to go
- have drinks/food ready so you don't have to get up to go get necessities
- have a clear idea of what you want to accomplish during the session (i.e., choose a task from your to-do list)


✧･ﾟ during the breaks:
- stop working as soon as the timer hits, even if you're mid-sentence
- make sure to get up, do some simple stretches
- refill anything that needs to get refilled
- talk to friends/update family

✧･ﾟ at the end of this video:
if you want to continue studying, give yourself a longer break and you can the next session video!

you're set to go! ♡
_____________________________
💡Please adjust the volume for each of the background music that comes out.
The ASMR that comes out with 💡 is the sound of burning wood and Rain. 
_____________________________

We have a Chat bot- 🤖
Commands for chat bot- 

!hi - when you join in👋
!start - to start studying
!top - Top Points
!points -  to know your points💯
!complete - when done with the goal

Chat rules:
- Being nice and respectful is mandatory!
- Spamming, harassment, trolling, bullying, repeating and all capital messages are definitely prohibited!
- Please feel encouraged to write in English so no one would feel excluded in the chat :)
- Please check YouTube's Community Guidelines
_____________________________

To those who are starting :
In order to study or do anything for long periods of time you need a strong purpose and you must be willing to endure challenges. If I can do this, think about what you can accomplish. If you're starting out, start from low intervals(10-30 minutes) and gradually increase once you feel you're comfortable. If you feel like quitting, visualize your goals and evaluate your purpose. Learn to accept challenges in your life to become uncommon.

S17.description:
Hellowzinho! 🥰

Keep me on the corner of your screen while you work in something else (another tab): double click with the right button on the video and select the option picture-in-picture! Doooone! Now we can stay together all the time! 😍

Nice to meet you and it's a pleasure to have your company here! 
My name is Brendha, I'm 27 years old and my dream is to become a doctor. 🩺❤️

🕑 Timezone: UTC - 3 (Horário de Brasília)

Q&A 👀

1. Where are you from?
I'm from Brazil 💚💛

2. What languages do you speak?
Portuguese and English

3. Who is Felipe Eduardo?
He's my husband ❤️

4. What are the names of your dogs?
We have five dogs: Moranga 🤍, Max 🧡, Mawi 🖤,  Morpheu 🖤🤍 and Fiapo 🧡🖤
It's because of them that I keep the rain backgroud sound and sometimes I have to turn off my mic... They have so much energy 🤪

5. When is your birthday?
July 30th

6. Did you study another course in college previously?
Yes, I studied Chemical Engineering for about 1 year and a half, but I decided to quit so I could focus in getting into med school, which was always my dream.

7. Are you already in med school?
Unfortunately, not yet. The entrance exam here in Brazil to get into med school is really hard and I've been preparing myself for it. I've got close, really close 😅, but it wasn't enough. So, right now, I'm studying for the entrance exam.

8. What is the meaning of 'bora'? 😄
'Bora' is a brazilian slang that we usually use when we want to say 'let's go!", so everytime we start a new session, we say BORA!!!! 😁 Very cheerful!

9. How does this study with me livestream work?
I'm here to help you to get motivated to study and to keep you company! Also, having your company here with me is super super super motivational, it helps me to get through the study day in a better way! ❤️ So, while I have online live classes, I won't take official breaks and I'll answer your messages whenever I can by the chat! During study sessions, we will study for 90 minutes (1h30)  or more and then take a break of 10 minutes, when we can rest and chat. During the day, I'll also may take long breaks to go to the gym, have lunch, take a shower, have dinner, do some chores (...), and the stream will keep going on during this time!

10. O que eu faço se sou brasileiro/brasileira?
Vem cá treinar esse inglês, meu bem!!!! Brincadeiras à parte, eu sempre falo em português com o pessoal e traduzo para o português o que estou falando em inglês quando há necessidade! Então, pode entrar e ficar à vontade, a casa é sua! 😁 E tenha certeza que seu inglês vai melhorar bastante se você praticar o listening (me ouvir) e o writing (escrever no chat) 😉

S20.title: 勉強動画 毎日24時間・日本初 study with me ポモドーロタイマー🍅 2025-04-03 15:45
S20.description:
この放送は 【１】日本初の勉強動画を24時間毎日放送 【２】YouTubeLiveを活用したオンライン自習室 【３】学習記録機能付きのチャット です。(最新のお知らせ: https://www.notion.so/manten120/1e3702349dcc4cdea53fcfc812d89ff9?pvs=4)

【１】

日本初！24時間毎日、勉強している姿を放送し続けるチャンネルです。

This is Japanese First 24/7/365 study broad cast

生放送と再放送を交互に行い24時間放送しています(2018年8月14日開始)

★10年間、毎日生放送します　※2028年まで。生放送の時間帯は主のライフスタイルの変化に応じて変わります。

★右下のタイマーは

⏰25分勉強(赤)

⏰5分休憩(緑)

を繰り返しています

4回目の休憩は20分です

🍅このタイマーによる勉強法をポモドーロ勉強法といいます🍅

🍅この放送では25分間の勉強を1回することを "1コマ勉強する" と数えています🍅

【２】

日本で初めてYouTubeLiveを活用したオンライン自習室(通称：満点ルーム)です！

配信主Mantenが運営するオンライン自習室(満点ルーム)で視聴者さんどうし一緒に勉強しませんか? 

スマホやウェブカメラで机をうつせば、あなたの部屋が世界中の人と一緒に勉強できる自習室になります。

たまにYouTubeにうつります。

満点ルームの運営管理は全て かずちゃむ (Twitter: https://twitter.com/kazchamu_manten ) ちゃんにお任せしております

満点ルームの使い方  https://manten120.notion.site/c31bd3cef255412da64be11334516d8d?pvs=4

【３】

世界初!! YoutubeLiveのチャットで学習の記録をつけられます！

コマンド(!25など)をチャットに書き込むことで学習記録をつけることができます。

満点学習帳 ( https://www.mantenroom.com ) と連携しています。

くわしくは上記リンクと下の 【コマンドの使い方】 にて。

【コマンドの使い方】

!25 など!で始まる単語をコマンドと言います。コマンドをチャットに書き込むとbot(自動返信ロボット🤖)を通じて学習の記録をつけられます。

!make

あなたの学習記録ページを作成します

学習記録ページはサイト満点学習帳 ( https://www.mantenroom.com )  に作成されます。

!home

あなたの学習記録ページのURLを返します

!25

1回25分の勉強回数(コマ数)を記録します

今日のコマ数と過去全期間の累計コマ数を返します

学習記録ページに反映されます

(!25aと!25bも同じ機能のコマンドです

ほかの人とタイミングがかぶると反応しないので、

かぶりやすいこのコマンドだけ3種類用意してます)

!delete

学習記録ページに関するすべてのデータを削除します😭

そのほか満点学習帳と連携するコマンドの一覧は『学習記録ページ → ? → 目標設定(仮) → ページ最下部』にて見れます。

ここまでのコマンドは主にコマルチャンbotが返信してくれます⛄

コマルチャンbotが担当するのは満点学習帳・学習記録・満点ルームに関するコマンドです。

満点ルームに関するコマンドは

!room

満点ルーム(オンライン自習室)でカメラをつけて利用した時間を表示する。満点ルームを利用していない人が使うと『0時間0分』と返信されます。

🤖🤖🤖🤖🤖

ここから下のコマンドはNight botが返信してくれます。Night botが担当するコマンドは満点学習帳・学習記録には記録されませんが、モチベを高めたるために自由に使ってくださいませ💨

!in

勉強開始の宣言

!out

勉強終了の宣言

!break 10

10分間の休憩と10分後に必ず戻ってくる宣言

数字は自由に変えられます

数字の前に半角スペースが必要です

他にもいろいろなコマンドがあるよ✨

他の人が使っているのを見て少しずつ覚えていこう！

(Night botが担当する全コマンドのリストはありません)

🤖🤖🤖🤖🤖

【その他】

★チャット欄では勉強に関する話題を書き込んで、視聴者さんどうし切磋琢磨しましょう。勉強から著しく逸脱する話題はNGです。

(これは放送主及びモデレーターによるチャット管理の指針です。発言の萎縮につながるため視聴者さんどうしで注意しあうことは極力お控えください) 

★初見さんは「半年ROMる」といいかも

(しばらく読むのだけに専念して、どんな書き込みが歓迎されるか、雰囲気がつかめるまで書き込みを控えること)

★視聴者さん同士の呼び名について

呼び捨ては禁止です。削除します。

「～と呼んでいいですか？」「～と呼んでください」等のコメントは禁止です。

★BGMは集中力を高める雨音です。ピアノサウンドもミックスしてあります。 

★モデレーター(満点モデレーターチーム)

チャットで名前が青くなっている人です。(Botを除く)

不適切発言の削除など、平和なチャットを保つため協力してくださっています

・なま茶さん(アットホームなチャット欄の礎を作った人)

・アイルーちゃん(適当大魔神。乙🍛の生みの親)

・うにちゃん(うにちゃん)

・*めい*ちゃん( ( ▔•з•▔ ) )

・うめしゅさん(うめちゃん)

・ラスカルはな.さん(餃子ガラの派手な服を持っている)

・茶ぽちゃん【ボン人】(水溜りボンド大好き♡)

・にゃんこちゃん(にゃんぽぽぽぽぽぽりーぬ)

・こまるちゃん (宝)

----- 過去在籍のモデレーターさん ----

・Rinさん

・AkkSさん

・本気で勉強頑張る!!!!!さん

・・Kurotan_ さん

----------------------------------------------------------

モデレーターさんに加え常連様のご協力によりすばらしいチャットになっています😃ありがとうございます✨


【満点ルーム注意事項】

・入室用URLをクリックし、最初のページでお名前を入力すると入室できます。スマホの場合、内カメラが起動するので注意。入室後歯車マークの設定画面で背面カメラに変えられます。

・入室する時のお名前はYouTubeアカウントと同名にしてください。

❤😷😷😷😷😷😷😷😷❤

😷  お顔が映らないように     😷

😷  マスクを必ず着用            😷

❤😷😷😷😷😷😷😷😷❤

・アーカイブ・録画残ります。再放送にも映りますので必ずマスク着用！ （マスクをすれば首から上を映していいという意味ではありません）

・ライブに映るのは基本的にルーム１だけです。

・すべてのルームの様子は動画として編集・投稿されることがあります。

🎤入室したらすぐにマイクをオフ🎤

・カメラマークを押せば一時的にカメラオフにできます

・お顔がうつっていたりマイクがオンのままなどの問題があるときは強制退室にしてお知らせします。注意事項をもういちど読みなおしてから入室してください。

・閲覧のみの目的で入室することは禁止です。

・Youtubeを見ながら映りたい場合、PCまたは複数の端末が必要です

・満員時など鍵をかける場合があります。パスワードは非公表です。

S71.description:
Hi! it's me Rahul 🙋

This is the study with me session and here we use the pomodoro technique for studying. Pomodoro technique is one of the most effective studying technique which helps you to boost your focus and productivity while studying. Here we apply the 60/10 format (60 minutes study and 10 minutes break). During break time feel free to chitchat with me in live chat. 

Don't forget to keep water bottle by your side and stay hydrated!



📌Basic information:

❔Which class do you study📚?
  :12

❔Where are you from?
  : Nepal🇳🇵

❔What's your age?
  :17

❔What subjects are you studying?
  : Chemistry, Physics, Maths, Especially for IPHO

❔College/university?
  : St.Xavier's College, Maitighar, Kathmandu, Nepal

❔Who is your inspirational figure?
  : Many people( it's difficult to name one)

❔Any book recommendations?
  : Atomic Habits, The Subtle Art Of Not Giving A F*ck, Deep Work 


Instagram
: https://www.instagram.com/_almostrahul_/
: https://www.instagram.com/_rahuldevkota/


For inquires
: rahulenter22@gmail.com





💭Thoughts and purpose of this channel:

In today's world it's so difficult to congregate your focus for a particular work. There are distractions everywhere and it's too easy to lose your self-consciousness to these distractions. During this period of engrossment, It becomes essential for us to take back our consciousness and get out of the pool of distractions which seems pleasureful to swim in but is slowly submerging us into it. Best way to avoid these things is to be conscious and engage yourself in the activity which is actually important to you. It is the exact purpose of this channel. This channel is rooted onto the foundation of making progress and helping other to make progress. 

Personally, I get motivated by watching other people study. I've been watching these "study with me" sessions of other youtubers from long ago (until I started my own), and being honest, it helped me a lot. I am heartily thankful for those youtubers who helped me to make my study effective and I can confront that they created a positive impact in my life. Since I'm in their place right now, I can't be more happier than to be able to make the same positive impact on other people's life. There is a quotation saying "Helping others is the way we help ourselves". I feel that helping people and being able to make a positive impact in other people's life is the greatest thing a human can do. So, I think that you have understood the soul purpose of creating this channel.

Also, not to forget that this channel is highly inspired by 'James Scholz' who is the original founder and god of 'Study with me' videos. 'Pascal Zoels', '7viksthan' are other popular YouTubers who post similar contents (ps. they are my favorite)
